GEORGE W. GREEN v. C. J. EARLY, as Trustee, et al. 22 So. (2nd) 466

January Term, 1945

June 1, 1945 Division A Carroll Dunscombe, for appellant. Arthur R. Clonts for Appellee Charles T. Kemble and T. T. Oughterson and Dewey Crawford for Rose Whitney, appellees. PER CURIAM:

No error appearing in the record the decree appealed from is affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
